<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Egypt" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Egypt,</orth> 1) country in Northern Africa: <cit><quote>a brow of E.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>all the first-born of E.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.5.63" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 5, 63</bibl></cit> (see <cit><quote>First-born). for all the mud in E.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 92</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. ant 1.1.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 1, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.5.12" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 12</bibl> etc.<lb />2) the king of Egypt: <cit><quote>--'s widow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 1, 37</bibl></cit> the queen of Egypt (Cleopatra): <bibl n="shak. ant 1.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 41</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ant 1.5.43" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 43</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.9.51" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 9, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.9.51" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 9, 51</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.14.15" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 14, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.15.18" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 15, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.15.18" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 15, 18</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.114" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 114</bibl>.
